<div class="company-list">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <img src="img/companyListBanner.png" alt="网速炸了" class="company-list-banner">
        </div>
        <div class="search-company">
            <form class="">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="search-title">公司地点：</label>
                    <a class="choseBoxes"
                       ng-class="{true:'beChosen',false:'cancelChoice'}[theCity.choose]"
                       ng-repeat="theCity in vm.city"
                       ng-click="vm.chooseCity($index,theCity.choose)"
                    >{{theCity.name}}</a>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="search-title">融资阶段：</label>
                    <a class="choseBoxes"
                       ng-class="{true:'beChosen',false:'cancelChoice'}[theFinancing.choose]"
                       ng-repeat="theFinancing in vm.financing"
                       ng-click="vm.chooseFinancing($index,theFinancing.choose)"
                    >{{theFinancing.name}}</a>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="search-title">行业领域：</label>
                    <a class="choseBoxes"
                       ng-class="{true:'beChosen',false:'cancelChoice'}[theIndustry.choose]"
                       ng-repeat="theIndustry in vm.industry"
                       ng-click="vm.chooseIndustry($index,theIndustry.choose)"
                    >{{theIndustry.name}}</a>
                </div>
            </form>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="pull-right">
                        <button class="btn btn-xs  choseBoxes btn-default   "
                                ng-click="vm.companyClear()">清除
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn btn-xs choseBoxes btn-danger"
                                ng-click="vm.companySearch()">搜索
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section class="row search-company-list">
            <div class="row" ng-hide="vm.result">
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 search-company-card"
                     ng-repeat="company in vm.companiesList"
                     ui-sref="home.companyDetail({id:company.id})">
                    <div class="search-company-content col-xs-12">
                        <div class="company-panel">
                            <div class="company-card">
                                <div class="company-logo">
                                    <img src="{{company.logo}}" alt="" class="company-img">
                                </div>
                                <div class="company-text">
                                    <p class="company-name">
                                        {{company.name}}
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="common-slogan">
                                        {{company.slogan}}
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="company-jobs">
                                        <span style="color: #fc2b47">{{company.professionNum}}</span>个在招职位
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="company-message">
                        <span class="">
                            <img src="img/companyListType.png" alt="">
                            <span>{{company.industryList[0]|industryList}}</span>
                        </span>
                                <span class="">
                            <img src="img/companyListfinancing.png" alt="">
                            <span>{{company.financing|financing}}</span>
                        </span>
                                <span class="">
                            <img src="img/companyListMap.png" alt="">
                            <span>{{company.city|region}}</span>
                        </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 page-config">
                    <pagination size="vm.size" page="vm.page" total="vm.total"></pagination>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-find" ng-hide="!vm.result">
                <div class="no-find-img">
                    <img src="img/alient.png" alt="网速炸了别看了">
                </div>
                <div class="no-find-text">
                <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #2b3d51">
                    <strong>暂时没有符合该搜索条件的内容</strong>
                </span><br>
                    <span style="font-size: 18px; color: #536a82">
                    <strong>请重新修改搜索条件后再次进行搜索</strong>
                </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

